data.name: Business Cash Reserve Savings
data.description: Earn interest on your collected GST and access your funds anytime you need them with our most popular business online savings account

features.additionalInfo: Unlimited transfers between other Westpac Business accounts held by customer in the same name(s) as the Westpac Business Cash Reserve account, using Business Online Banking or automated Group Telephone Banking only
Opt for eco-friendly free eStatements and access up to seven years of transactions without the clutter.
Export your transactions - Save time and money by exporting transactions to your existing accounting software from Westpac Online
Tiered interest is paid on certain balances
Interest is paid on monthly basis
You have choice of 3 or 6 monthly statements.
Account enquiries are always free when you use Online Banking.

eligibility.additionalValue: Operating in Australia with an Australian address

eligibility.additionalInfo: Eligible entities include sole traders, partnerships, companies, associations, self-managed super funds, trusts and not-for-profit organisations
Must not be an individual using the account for predominantly personal purposes
Needs an eligible Westpac business transaction account to link to.

fees.name: Self-Service (Electronic) Withdrawals
fees.additionalInfo: Nil for withdrawals from the account to a Westpac Business account held in the same name(s) as the account. Otherwise, such withdrawal will incur $5.00 fee per withdrawal.

fees.name: Cheques Collected / Deposited
fees.additionalInfo: Cheques collected or deposited (Additional charge for the branch transaction applies)

fees.name: Staff-Assisted Withdrawal
fees.additionalInfo: These channels are not available, however if these transactions occur for each transaction a $5.00 fee will be incurred.

fees.name: Narrated Credits
fees.additionalInfo: These channels are not available, however if these transactions occur for each transaction a $2.50 fee will be incurred.

fees.name: Periodical Payments
fees.additionalInfo: Additional fees apply for Periodical Payments made by Bank Cheque and International Periodical Payments. These channels are not available, however if these transactions occur for each transaction a $5.00 fee will be incurred.

fees.name: Online Banking
fees.additionalInfo: Account enquiries are always free when you use Online Banking.

depositRates.additionalValue: For balances up to $30,000, you'll receive a bonus rate on your Business Cash Reserve savings account - earning up to 2.05% p.a. for the first 12 months. Accounts opened from 17th June 2024. Eligibility criteria and T&Cs apply. If you already have a Business One Plus and a Business Cash Reserve account, you?re ineligible.
